tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE community_engagement (
    initiative_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    coordinator_name VARCHAR(100),
    budget NUMERIC(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE community_engagement_initiatives (
    initiative_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    target_audience VARCHAR(100),
    status VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'Planned'
);

CREATE TABLE stakeholder_feedback (
    feedback_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT NOT NULL REFERENCES community_engagement_initiatives(initiative_id),
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    submission_date TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE community_engagement_initiatives (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name TEXT,
    stakeholder_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE initiative_participants (
    participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT,
    participant_name TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    role TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (initiative_id) REFERENCES community_engagement_initiatives(id)
)

CREATE TABLE stakeholder_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT,
    participant_id INT,
    feedback TEXT,
    submission_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (initiative_id) REFERENCES community_engagement_initiatives(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES initiative_participants(participant_id)
)

CREATE TABLE community_engagement (
    initiative_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE stakeholders (
    stakeholder_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stakeholder_name VARCHAR(255),
    organization VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE initiatives_progress (
    progress_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT,
    stakeholder_id INT,
    progress_status VARCHAR(50),
    progress_update TEXT,
    update_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT,
    stakeholder_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    feedback_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE community_engagement_initiatives (
    initiative_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    stakeholder_group VARCHAR(100),
    description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE stakeholders (
    stakeholder_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stakeholder_name VARCHAR(255),
    contact_email VARCHAR(255),
    organization VARCHAR(255),
    role VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE initiatives_participants (
    participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_name VARCHAR(255),
    initiative_id INT,
    stakeholder_id INT,
    role VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE initiative_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT,
    stakeholder_id INT,
    feedback_date DATE,
    feedback TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE initiative_evaluation (
    evaluation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT,
    evaluation_date DATE,
    evaluator VARCHAR(255),
    rating INT
)
